The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for learning bilingual dictionaries. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses unsupervised learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses word embeddings, which are a popular technique in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses information retrieval techniques for evaluating the performance of the proposed method, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses techniques for aligning vector spaces, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV).
